SYSTEM: The Ruins of Elis hold a place in Calcedonian lore as a place of death. Although it is home to nothing but wild dogs and abandoned catacombs of ancient wars, not even the bravest wildersmen dare enter the grounds. Rumors have reached HERO-FULL in Labrynne that tell of a palatial mansion erected in the midst of the ruins, seemingly appearing overnight.\nNone know the identity of the master of the house, but a mission from the Calcedonian throne prompts SECOND-FULL to bring HERO as well as IDIOT-FULL and SNARKY-FULL to the Gates of the Manor of Elis, to uncover the mystery within.